title: Wrong typing at documentation
body_html:
I think there is an typing error:
http://pytorch.org/docs/autograd.html

It should be a sequence of matching length, that containins gradient of the differentiated function w.r.t. corresponding variables (None is an acceptable value for all variables that don’t need gradient tensors).

body:
I think there is an typing error:
http://pytorch.org/docs/autograd.html

It should be a sequence of matching length, that **containins** gradient of the differentiated function w.r.t. corresponding variables (None is an acceptable value for all variables that don’t need gradient tensors).
